* TODO Various MIME types should be supported, and the user should be able to specify a list of MIME types for which the module should be active.
* FIXME Spaces eaten before an HREF tag are not compensated for.
Currently,
     This is a <a href="...">link</a>
gets served as
     This is a<a href="...">link</a>
because the space eaten before the link is not compensated for.
This should be fixed by representing genuine spaces as &#32 instead of ' '
